Fixed stability issues with iOS 13. Fixed bug where photos were not loading properly when creating a new entry. Fixed bug where the main entry photo was not appearing in a PDF export. Fixed bug where Random sort was not working properly. Faster backups to iCloud and Dropbox. Thanks to all for trying GRATEFUL and especially for your emails and feedback. We are listening! apps treebetty.com

NEW PHOTO CROPPING TOOL: Adjust how your photos will be saved and displayed in your entries using the new crop tool. BACKUP REMINDERS: You will now get backup reminders if you haven t backed up your journal in the past 5 days. If you d prefer not to receive these you can turn them off in the SETTINGS. As always thanks for using GRATEFUL. A big thanks to all who have left ratings and reviews as well. It s a huge help.

Lots of new features! Photo Ipdates: View and save up to 5 photos per entry. View multiple photos from feed by swiping between photos. Force touch to open in a full window. Photos taken within the app are now saved to your device s Camera Roll. PDF Export Updates: Choose a date range for exporting your entries. The PDF has been revised to fit larger text entries. You can now export your PDF directly to your. Exporting your journal to a CSV file is now possible. And More: Tags now displayed in your journal feed. Turn this on off in SETTINGS . Backup and restore your data with iCloud. Dark background now uses a dark keyboard. Passcode now works with Face ID. Other News: GRATEFUL is now part of our new Growth Bundle. Get discounted premium access to our most popular productivity and lifestyle apps. Look for What s the Growth Bundle in the SETTINGS to learn more. Thanks to all for trying GRATEFUL and especially for your emails feedback and reviews. We are listening! apps treebetty.com

Some users have reported that sometimes reminders suddenly stop working. This update fixes those reminder problems. Thanks to all for trying GRATEFUL and especially for your emails feedback and reviews. We are listening! apps treebetty.com

iPhone X Support. Thanks for your patience! Touch ID now working with the passcode There s now landscape mode for iPad New customizable reminders with more sounds and a snooze option App sounds on off now working

There s now a Grateful widget. Be reminded of random moments of gratitude without even opening the app. You can now add tags or categories to your entries. You can then sort your journal feed by these tags. Export your journal in PDF format so you can print it. The PDF format has the same clean simple design as the app. Premium feature . Now you can crop your photos to better fit the journal feed format. Easily share an entry with friends via email SMS and Facebook. Click on the share icon on when viewing an entry in page format . Search for entries based on keywords. New journal feed text sizes small medium and large. The default size is medium. Sort your journal feed randomly and be reminded of past happy moments. You can now save your photos in either low resolution or high resolution format. Choose high resolution if you plan on printing your journal . Thanks to all for trying GRATEFUL and especially for your emails and feedback. We are listening! apps treebetty.com

Dropbox Integration : You can now backup your journal and photos to Dropbox. Premium only Added a new DARK background mode to make journaling at night easier on the eyes Button sound effects can now be turned ON and OFF
